item.title: Prayer bpn10862 in Tuvalu
item.description: ##KE FAI FAKA-TASI I TE SEFULU-FA ITULA *A ia te la e fai ne ia a te talo tenei, e tu a ia ki luga kae saga atu ki te Atua, ite koga te la e tu a ia, ke saga atu ona mata kite faka-matua mo te fakamaui, pela loa a ia e faitalitali ki te alofa-kaimalie o tena Aliki, te Toe Alofa-Kaimalie Katoatoa, te Alofa-Atafai.
